THE day that Somizi and Mohale’s glitzy traditional wedding has Mzansi jubilant about their union. TV host and choreographer Somizi Mhlongo (46) got hitched to his sweetheart Mohale Motaung (24) today and the guests were sipping on some champopo courtesy of Bonang Matheba’s House of BNG. The couple recently celebrated their second anniversary, the love birds have been together since 2017. Musicians like Judith Sephuma, Brenda Mtambo , Vusi Nova, Lerato Kganyago performed at the much anticipated wedding.       